{
  "is_npc": true,
  "short_description": "Ready? Aim and fire.",
  "long_description": "COOL FOR: TRICK-SHOOTERS. SNIPERS. JUGGLERS.\n\nHand / Eye Coordination loves the interactions between you and things that fly in the air. It enables you to catch coins from mob bosses, shoot straight, and understand firearms intimately. Want to know the precise make and mark of a pistol? H/E Coordination's got you. Want to shoot someone with it? Ditto.\n\nAt high levels, Hand / Eye Coordination makes you deadly – supposing you’ve a weapon in your hand. But once you do, H/E Coordination will compel you to take the shot – even if it’s not the best approach. At low levels, however, you’ll be even more of a disaster in waiting. Because when the guns go off – and they always do – you’ll probably hit the wrong target.",
  "color": 5
}

